                     <hi rend="largeCaps">JEREMIAH COCKLIN</hi> (30)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18710403-299-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18710403-299-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18710403-299-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, Stealing a medal and 17<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18710403-name-202" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18710403-name-202" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
